<lyrics>[V1]
 Hmasa phungbia in luatnak cu a tha, Jesuh a thi thlet in khamhnak kan
 hmuh, Adam chiatserh sualnak ka chung in, Jesuh a kan khamh lai nihin.

[C1]
   A kan khamh cang, Maw misual zum tuah, A kan khamh cang, Unau zum
   tuah u, Hreng-khenh hngat in thilrit a thumh lai, Jesuh nih a kan khamh
   cang lai.

[V2]
 Sualnak in kannih nih kan luat cang lai, Jesuh khamhnak fiang tein a
 lang cang, &quot;Ka sinah ra,&quot; ti in a kan auh, Ra tuah, atu a kan khamh lai.

[C2]
   A kan khamh cang, Maw misual zum tuah, A kan khamh cang, Unau zum
   tuah u, Hreng-khenh hngat in thilrit a thumh lai, Jesuh nih a kan khamh
   cang lai.

[V3]
 Pathian fale kan si ca lawmhnak in, Tukforhnak kha kan i sum kho lai
 ta, Thihnak kan in, lu nun kan hmuh cang, Lu nun khamhnak thluachuah a si.

[C3]
   A kan khamh cang, Maw misual zum tuah, A kan khamh cang, Unau zum
   tuah u, Hreng-khenh hngat in thilrit a thumh lai, Jesuh nih a kan khamh
   cang lai.</lyrics>
<title>A ZUNGZAL CA VOI KHAT LAWNG CH263</title>
<hymn_number>263</hymn_number>
</song>